queries.sql: select * from `sliders` where `channel_id` = 1 and find_in_set('en', locale) and (`expired_at` >= '2021-06-11' or `expired_at` is null)

select `locales`.*, `channel_locales`.`channel_id` as `pivot_channel_id`, `channel_locales`.`locale_id` as `pivot_locale_id` from `locales` inner join `channel_locales` on `locales`.`id` = `channel_locales`.`locale_id` where `channel_locales`.`channel_id` = 1

select `currencies`.*, `channel_currencies`.`channel_id` as `pivot_channel_id`, `channel_currencies`.`currency_id` as `pivot_currency_id` from `currencies` inner join `channel_currencies` on `currencies`.`id` = `channel_currencies`.`currency_id` where `channel_currencies`.`channel_id` = 1

select distinct `velocity_contents`.`content_type`, `velocity_contents_translations`.`title` as `title`, `velocity_contents_translations`.`page_link` as `page_link`, `velocity_contents_translations`.`link_target` as `link_target` from `velocity_contents` left join `velocity_contents_translations` on `velocity_contents`.`id` = `velocity_contents_translations`.`content_id` where `velocity_contents`.`status` = 1 and `velocity_contents_translations`.`locale` = 'en' order by `position` asc limit 8

statements.sql: select * from `sliders` where `channel_id` = 1 and find_in_set('en', locale) and (`expired_at` >= '2021-06-11' or `expired_at` is null)
select * from `channel_translations` where `channel_translations`.`channel_id` = 1 and `channel_translations`.`channel_id` is not null

select `locales`.*, `channel_locales`.`channel_id` as `pivot_channel_id`, `channel_locales`.`locale_id` as `pivot_locale_id` from `locales` inner join `channel_locales` on `locales`.`id` = `channel_locales`.`locale_id` where `channel_locales`.`channel_id` = 1

select `currencies`.*, `channel_currencies`.`channel_id` as `pivot_channel_id`, `channel_currencies`.`currency_id` as `pivot_currency_id` from `currencies` inner join `channel_currencies` on `currencies`.`id` = `channel_currencies`.`currency_id` where `channel_currencies`.`channel_id` = 1

select distinct `velocity_contents`.`content_type`, `velocity_contents_translations`.`title` as `title`, `velocity_contents_translations`.`page_link` as `page_link`, `velocity_contents_translations`.`link_target` as `link_target` from `velocity_contents` left join `velocity_contents_translations` on `velocity_contents`.`id` = `velocity_contents_translations`.`content_id` where `velocity_contents`.`status` = 1 and `velocity_contents_translations`.`locale` = 'en' order by `position` asc limit 8
